Suddenly a mysterious stasis pod lands on earth out in the forest.  All is 
silent, while the land is scanned for a life form.  A panther is found!  
Suddenly the pod bursts open and a new warrior is formed! ... SHADOW STALKER. 
 As hes stepping out of the pod he decides to test out his robot mode.  
"Satisfying... indeed."  He walks out, curious is to finding any other robots 
such as him.
